{"tid":696155,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"紅塵夢醒──調寄《紅塵客棧》","createTime":"2018-06-09T21:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T07:02:08.000Z","uid":190178,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9e41e1cddcd02c05970ef0f93c004eea22d6ef19","tid":696155,"uid":190178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T21:28:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/678079/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/678079/page/1</a><br />\n睇見同台有post都填《紅塵客棧》，小弟都忍唔住冒昧開post，貼返舊作出嚟。新手開post，多多指教。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n曲唱：周杰倫<br />\n原詞：方文山<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L6joGUdc6y4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL6joGUdc6y4&d=zGVRLTQBPH4w8ArbeQXnJuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=30701f85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L6joGUdc6y4</a><br />\n　<br />\n霧雨伴煙洗滌浮華<br />\n恨愛　分分秒秒惦掛<br />\n覓尋萬里再找不到這般細沙<br />\n無力強裝瀟灑<br />\n　<br />\n避世　萬般都點不化<br />\n入世　驚悉了世道可怕<br />\n誓言道破最終都不過長留疤印<br />\n恨極我癡心不知詐<br />\n　<br />\n＊而回憶曾如詩似畫<br />\n境遷了愁思沉澱皆垣瓦<br />\n仍然未慣當孤家<br />\n舊情斷淚忍下<br />\n　<br />\n笑語不忍聽　莫再　去想誰有心作假<br />\n瀟瀟雨何苦如恆久不休<br />\n故夢了看風破<br />\n已力歇長夜一早聲沙＊<br />\n　<br />\n白雪傍巾鶯聲淺笑<br />\n獨作翩翩氣宇儒雅<br />\n乍寒靜聽老鴉　心苦惱　今悔昔<br />\n前塵無助栽花<br />\n　<br />\n自困在山邊不招架<br />\n柔情蜜意　水東去　腦內消散<br />\n密雲敗柳底相分苦別門前一剎<br />\n發現了心底　滿是她<br />\n　<br />\n＊<br />\n　<br />\n笑語不忍聽　莫再　去想誰那麼虛假<br />\n天真太無知　如藏井之蛙<br />\n回頭未放低牽掛<br />\n念那癡癡剎那<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n順便賣個廣告，啱睇嘅like埋page吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bullsword/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbullsword%2F&d=zGVRLTQBPH4w8ArbeQXnJuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=709ce8bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bullsword/</a>"},{"pid":"3dda514af879bc34d0909eece39422fd31451f5f","tid":696155,"uid":56240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T04:09:59.000Z","msg":"押韻全部一樣音"},{"pid":"0098b2d6a9e4838a5cf25b51ee2a3bb409556794","tid":696155,"uid":190178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dda514af879bc34d0909eece39422fd31451f5f","tid":696155,"uid":56240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T04:09:59.000Z","msg":"押韻全部一樣音"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T05:10:53.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪-aa韻配搭少，尤其是第三、五調&hellip;&hellip;開頭「洗滌浮華」有少少拗，但係都叫做轉下調多少少變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4bd248e45cada65760e6b17084141ca5fc948c","tid":696155,"uid":190178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0098b2d6a9e4838a5cf25b51ee2a3bb409556794","tid":696155,"uid":190178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dda514af879bc34d0909eece39422fd31451f5f","tid":696155,"uid":56240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T04:09:59.000Z","msg":"押韻全部一樣音"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T05:10:53.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪-aa韻配搭少，尤其是第三、五調&hellip;&hellip;開頭「洗滌浮華」有少少拗，但係都叫做轉下調多少少變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T05:12:02.000Z","msg":"係咁唔拉更咁嗎到尾又「傻的嗎」"},{"pid":"f0a53ca240e56b87202d6707f1e3f3303676d437","tid":696155,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dda514af879bc34d0909eece39422fd31451f5f","tid":696155,"uid":56240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T04:09:59.000Z","msg":"押韻全部一樣音"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"係押同一個韻吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但嚴格上aa、剎、散係三個唔同嘅韻，不過因類近所以可以通韻用咁解<br />\n呢個亦係aa韻富彈性嘅好玩之處<br />\nBtw支持多啲人玩改詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d6c144bdd20cbcb62d5152f62816266fbaebc2","tid":696155,"uid":26878,"like":1,"